---
globs: ["**/lib/supabase*", "**/lib/db*", "**/*migration*", "**/supabase/**"]
---

# MagByte Supabase rules

- Never disable RLS on any table
- Write a migration SQL file before any schema change
- analyzed_data is the source of truth — never truncate without confirmation
- Use service role key only in server-side code, never in client components
- Connection strings come from .env.local exclusively
- Prefer Supabase RPC for complex queries over raw SQL in components
